ghts. These weights say, in effect, =E2=80=9Chow relevant is every other wo=
rd to me?=E2=80=9D The model then builds a weighted average of value vector=
s, giving token i a focused, context-aware representation. Multiple attenti=
on =E2=80=9Cheads=E2=80=9D look for different patterns simultaneously=E2=80=
=94syntax, coreference, timeline cues, etc.
Feed-forward network: After attention mixes information, a small neural net=
work within the layer transforms each token independently, adding non-linea=
